quran[62]{c,v,t}:
  53,1,E hoodere si konde fukkiima
  53,2,Gondiijo mon majjaani o bewaa√Īi
  53,3,O haalata belaa…óe
  53,4,"Ndee [Alqur‚Äôaanaare] wonaali, si wanaa waaju bahyatee…óo"
  53,5,Ko jom semmbe janngini …óum mbo
  53,6,Jom mbaadi njoondi o fotondiri
  53,7,Hombo e jookli toow…ói
  53,8,Refti o …ďadi o …ďattii
  53,9,O woni …ďadii…óo fotde laanye …ói…óe wolla ko …ďuri …ďadaade
  53,10,O wahyii e maccu…óo makko ko O wahyii ko
  53,11,…ďernde mum fennaani ko o yi*i ko
  53,12,mbela ha…óa yeddandira e Mum ko O yi*i
  53,13,Ko noon tigi o yi*ii Jibriir laawol go…óngol
  53,14,ka lekki sidar njani sanne
  53,15,ka kiin lekki woni aljanna ko…óir…óo
  53,16,Nde muurata e lekki sidra-he ko naatata
  53,17,Yitere oon√Īaaki nde yawtaani keerol
  53,18,Ko goonga o yi*ii e kaawsaaji Alla …ďur…ói mawnude
  53,19,Onon heefer…ďe mbela on nji*ii laata e ujjaa
  53,20,E manaata tata…ďiija go…ó…óo o
  53,21,Mbela na woodani on gorko na woodani Mbo debbo
  53,22,…óuum de wadde ko feccoore nde nuun…óaani
  53,23,…ói ngonah si wonah in…óe …óe innu…óon onon e baabiraa…ďe mon Alla jippinaani heen daliil …ďe ndewaani si wonah sikke e mbelamme pittaali ko goongo peewal arii e ma…ď…ďe ummaade to Joom mum en
  53,24,wolla mbela na woodani ne…ó…óo ko o woo…óa ko
  53,25,Ko Alla woodani ko sakkati e ko adii
  53,26,Heewii e malaykaaji e nder kammuuji …ói tefoore majji nafatah huunde tawi wonah caggal de Alla sakkitani wonande mbo O wela O
  53,27,Pellet …ďeen …ďe ngoon…óinaani laakira ho…ďe innira malaykaaji in…óe rew…ďe
  53,28,"Woodanaani …ďe ganndal, alah kove ndewata si wonah sikke, pellet sikke nafatah e goonga hay huunde"
  53,29,…óuurno oon nduntii…óa jikru amen mbo yi…óah si wonah nguurndam aduna
  53,30,"Ko …óoon ganndal mum en haa…ói, pellet ko Alla …ďuri anndude oon majju…óo laawol Makko, ko Kanko kadi …ďuri anndude oon peew…óo"
  53,31,"Ko Alla woodani kala ko woni e kammuuji e leydi ngam o yo…ďa …ďeen bonnu…ďe ko…ďe mbonni ko, O yo…ďa kadi mo∆ī∆īin…ďe ko mo∆ī∆īi"
  53,32,"…ďen wo…ó…óitotoo…ďe bakkatuuji maw…ói …óin e pankare […ďe faggitotaako] si wanaa tokoosi …óin. Pellet, Joomi maa ko yaaju…óo yaafuyee. Ko Kanko …ďuri anndude on gila O fu…ó…óunoo on ummaade e leydi, e nde wonuno…óon fu∆ī∆īannde ka deedi neeniraa…ďe mon. Wata on mantu ko'e mon; ko Kanko …ďuri anndude gom…óu…ďe …ďen"
  53,33,E a tinaali …óuurnii…óo on
  53,34,"hino okka see…óaa, hooti o …óawa"
  53,35,Kere o jogi ganndal wirnii…ói ngal o yiirata
  53,36,Kaa o humpitaaka ko woni kon e …óeri Muusa …óin
  53,37,"e [ka …óeri] Ibraahiima hunnu…óo [ahadi yottini]"
  53,38,"wonnde wonkii [woo] ronndotaako doŇčgal (bakkaatu) wokkii goo"
  53,39,"e wonnde alanaa ne…ó…óanke, si wonaa ko o golli kon"
  53,40,"e wonnde golle makko …óen, aray ka yi'ee"
  53,41,refti o yo…ďiree …óe njo…ďdi timmundi
  53,42,e wonnde ko ka Joomi maa woni haattirde nden
  53,43,e wonnde ko Kanko woni Weltinoowo Wullina
  53,44,ko Kanko kadi woni Warooro Wuurnita
  53,45,"e wonnde O tagii resindiray…ói …óin …ói…ói : gorel e deyel"
  53,46,immorde e to…ď…ďere maniiyu si rufaama
  53,47,e wonnde ko Kanko woodani tagitugol …óimmun
  53,48,e wonnde ko Kanko woni al…óin…óo e okk…óu…óo
  53,49,e wonnde ko Kanko woni Jey…óo hoodere Si'ira nden
  53,50,e wonnde ko Kanko halki Aadi'en adinoo…ďe
  53,51,"e Samuuda'en, O heddinaano hay e gooto"
  53,52,"Ko non kadi yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen ko adii[…ďe], pellet, …ďen laatino …ďur…ďe too√Īude e bewde"
  53,53,e yim…ďe fitaare …ďen (…ďe) O waylitunoo
  53,54,O hippiri …óe kon ko O hippiri
  53,55,Ko hon…óum e neemaaji Joomi ma …óin sikkitoto…óaa
  53,56,Awa oo ko jertinoowo jeyaa…óo e jertinoo…ďe adinoo…ďe
  53,57,Darngal ngal non …ďadike
  53,58,"Du√Īoowo ngal ko woori Allah, alaa"
  53,59,"E ko ndee yewtere [Alqur'aana] haaweto…óon"
  53,60,"Hi…óon jala, on wullataa"
  53,61,Hara ko on welsindii…ďe
  53,62,"Koni sujjanee Allah, rewon [Mo]"